            <th>description</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr>
            <td><a href="http://www.jstree.com/documentation/html_data" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer">HTML_DATA plugin</a></td>
            <td>enables jsTree to convert nested unordered lists to interactive trees, an already existing UL may be used or data could be retrieved from a server</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td><a href="http://www.jstree.com/documentation/json_data" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer">JSON_DATA plugin</a></td>
            <td>enables jsTree to convert JSON objects to interactive trees, data can be set up in the config or retrieved from a server.</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
